nodes.text: Codo Keburr was a male Thisspiasian with a white beard. Sometime after the Battle of Yavin, he, Killaen Chamat, and Omi Vass searched a temple on Malian for a holocron. Keburr was wounded by a guardian droid.
Codo Keburr appears in the opening story of Fantasy Flight Games' 2018 roleplaying game sourcebook Unlimited Power.
